OL,6,GThere was an awkward moment at the
OL,7,Gstart of the weather segment on the BBC
OL,8,GNews at One today, when a studio guest
OL,9,Ggot in the way of the camera shot.
OL,11,FEconomics correspondent Andy Verity was
OL,12,Fseated at the Studio E desk for a brief
OL,13,Fdiscussion with presenter Jane Hill on
OL,14,Fthe programme's final story.
OL,16,FDiscussion complete and it was time to
OL,17,Fpop across to the catwalk for the
OL,18,Fweather, with Tomasz Schafernaker.
