OL,6,FAs usual, when we transition to the
OL,7,Fweather segment, we get a wide shot of
OL,8,Fthe studio. But something's not quite
OL,9,Fright.
OL,11,FThe floor manager is seen waving
OL,12,Ffrantically to catch Andy Verity's
OL,13,Fattention. Presumably she's been
OL,14,Finformed by the director that Andy is
OL,15,Fobstructing the camera shot of the
OL,16,Fweather presenter.
OL,18,FWhen we then cut to the weather camera,
OL,19,Fthe back of Andy's head is in shot.
OL,20,FAfter a few seconds, he moves out of
OL,21,Fthe way.
